  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eat your siblings in this whacky local couch multiplayer!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this local couch-multiplayer game, you step into the shoes of none other than Hannibal Lecker, who is chowing down on his siblings while still cozy in their mother's womb. You nibble away at your opponents' limbs by wiggling around and grabbing onto them until they're completely eaten. May the hungriest Hannibal Lecker win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Local Multiplayer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A training mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Hand drawn visuals</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Whacky physics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Juicy limb eating gameplay</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eat your siblings in this whacky local couch multiplayer!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this local couch-multiplayer game, you step into the shoes of none other than Hannibal Lecker, who is chowing down on his siblings while still cozy in their mother's womb. You nibble away at your opponents' limbs by wiggling around and grabbing onto them until they're completely eaten. May the hungriest Hannibal Lecker win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Local Multiplayer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A training mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Hand drawn visuals</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Whacky physics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Juicy limb eating gameplay</p>",
